Copper, Iron Ore, Oil Are Top Apollo Commodity Picks, Beard Says

-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 
2011-02-15T13:40:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/copper-iron-ore-oil-are-top-apollo-commodity-picks-beard-says.html
Copper, iron ore, coking coal and
oil are top commodity picks at Apollo Capital Management LLC,
Greg Beard, a senior partner at the New York-based private-
equity firm, said in an interview in Geneva today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Kolesnikova in Geneva at  mkolesnikova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
